So you really do feel like the very best resolution to that conflict was a race?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> We've never passed down the chance to add our forces when we didn't get there first.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
