<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  And I respected my friend enough to not only to be there for him, but to take part in something I personally detest (the roll), because it was the *right thing to do*<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
