<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  What's disrespectful about being prepared, ready, and raring to go invade France, while those 6 guys stand by the side of the road trying to recruit an army?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
